Femi Folaranmi, Yenagoa Three persons including two members of the National Youth Service Corps (NYSC) have been shot dead in Yenagoa, Bayelsa State capital by rampaging cultists. The cultists who have practically turned Yenagoa into a theatre of war also killed a pupil of a yet to be identified primary school. Eye-witness account said the police came to move the bodies of the deceased to the Federal Medical Centre (FMC) morgue.